            "body": "<p>The <code>validateItemquantity()<\/code> method should return a true or false, based on whether the input is valid or not. <\/p>\n\n<p>You can take care of the true and false cases in the function calling it. \nTo take input, you could show an input dialog maybe.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String text = JOptionPane.showInputDialog (\"Enter New Value\"));\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 13033348,
