            "creation_date": 1351004384,
            "body": "<p>I think the loop should be in the calling method.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>boolean validateItemquantity() {\n    try{ \n        Integer.parseInt(itemQuantityinput.getText());\n        return true; \n    }\n    catch (NumberFormatException e) {\n        JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, \"Item quantity must be a positive number, please reenter\");\n        error = false; \n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>And the calling part should be something like that<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>while(!validateItemquantity())\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 13033396,
            "question_id": 13033178
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/94mm8.png?s=256",
                "account_id": 1318407,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 1264768,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1264768/salbeira",
